[*] --> OnHold
OnHold --> Archived : reject
OnHold : entry / log deposit
Archived --> Pending : submit
Pending --> Approved : review
Approved --> Closed : submit
Approved : entry / log deposit
Closed --> Rejected : cancel
Closed --> Archived : revert
Rejected --> [*]
